comment: This was an amazing experience! I learned so much about AI and got to work on real projects. The team was incredibly supportive.
Great internship. The work was challenging, but I wish there was a bit more mentorship from senior data scientists.
The advanced React course was fantastic. The explanations were clear and the projects were very practical.
Good introductory course, but some of the later modules felt a bit rushed. Overall, a solid foundation in Python for data science.
